;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502060101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502060101.json-->
::'''Mr. Huo:''' All the most priceless treasures are in my... Oh, what a pleasant surprise! What brings you here today?
::'''Mr. Huo:''' You're a new face here. Never been to Aurum Alley before, I guess?
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Come in, come in! I have all sorts of wondrous treasures here! May I interest you with something?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wondrous treasures? You talk pretty big...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060106-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Well, well. My store may seem lackluster at first glance, but it's because I don't spend all my budget on fluffy marketing unlike those popular stores in Starskiff Haven.
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Cutting costs on decorations so I can buy genuine stock is the secret to getting the best stuff.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wondrous treasures? Won't they cost a fortune?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060109-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Ohh, that's not the case here. Everything here is sold at a fair price. We small businesses need to attract regulars, which isn't gonna happen if I set my prices sky-high!
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Besides, if you really think my stuff is too expensive... you're always welcome to stop by, take a look, and help us set a fairer price! You're welcome either way!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
