::'''Mr. Huo:''' I hope you can use these cycranes that I modified. They're different from the Heron Express cycranes...
::'''Mr. Huo:''' With my cycranes, {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|the longer the planned route, the higher the logistic score}}. You ready?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's get the planning started.
