;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Has business been going well lately?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502060401: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502060401.json-->
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Thanks to you, it's not bad... Nothing much has changed since the revival of the Aurum Alley, but my business is thriving.
::'''Mr. Huo:''' My customer base pretty much stays the same, but the sources of my goods have become more diverse.
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Nowadays outworld traveling merchants come here from time to time, all of them with rare goods that are hard to sell tucked under their coats...
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Here's a piece of wisdom for you: There are no bad goods, but only bad salespersons. As you are a capable person, I'd like to learn from you.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502060401-->
;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to ask...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502060201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502060201.json-->
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Don't be a stranger. Feel free to ask me anything.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502060201_648-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502060201_648-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What's your store's specialty?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060204-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Let me tell you all about it. Here you'll find nothing but the most unusual treasures, and my motto is "one-of-a-kind." I might not be able to claim that everything in the store is the only copy in the universe, but at least you won't find them anywhere else in the Xianzhou.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Are these rags what you call "wondrous treasures"?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060206-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' These "rags" may look old and cheap, but their histories are anything but ordinary. They are either lost artifacts or precious medicines that can only be obtained from the jaws of death.
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Only their fated owner can realize their priceless value. If none of my stuff catches your eye, perhaps they are simply not destined to be yours.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Will anyone really buy your stuff?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060209-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Hey, what are you trying to imply? Even if my store is rarely frequented by walk-in customers, I have my channels and connections for distribution.
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Besides, everyone knows me as someone specializing in rare goods. I have plenty of stable customers... Never mind. Don't you worry your pretty little head about this. These are business secrets.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any more questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060212-->
:::'''Mr. Huo:''' Alright. See you later.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
