:::<!--Custom String Listener: Finishlevelgraph-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Finishlevelgraph-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Finishlevelgraph-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502060201-->
;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} It's nothing. I shouldn't keep you.
::'''Mr. Huo:''' No problem. If you ever need anything in my line of trade, just let me know.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(Unused &mdash; TalkSentence_502060214)
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502060214-->
::'''Mr. Huo:''' Heh, it's not like I'm squeezing my customers... Buying low and selling high is a merchant's bounden duty. They keep calling me a greedy merchant, but all merchants are greedy, aren't they?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
